{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839876698,"sessionID":"ses_287b27750ffehZARaHhI67wI2a","part":{"id":"prt_d784de548001ckhmhP1AJ5DMrp","messageID":"msg_d784dd60d0015slmIx7DHJP09A","sessionID":"ses_287b27750ffehZARaHhI67wI2a","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_c9c2af65389a482c8554a22c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-002\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n### AR-002-001: CodeInterpreter type definition\n\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreter` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n\n### AR-002-002: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining spec fields\n- **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL be of type `AuthMode` (enum: \"picod\", \"none\"), optional, default `\"picod\"`\n- **AND** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"8h\"`\n- **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"15m\"`\n- **AND** `Ports` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, optional\n- **AND** `Template` SHALL be of type `ContainerTemplateSpec`, required\n- **AND** `WarmPoolSize` SHALL be `int32` type, optional, default `0`\n\n### AR-002-003: CodeInterpreterStatus with ready field\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining status subresource\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n- **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Ready` of type `bool`\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n- AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n- API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775839876667,"end":1775839876694}}}}
